[{"Id": 1018140, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "[Print Ariza-3 {Print Ariza-3}]", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "[Print Ariza-3 {Print Ariza-3}]", "UrduDescription": "[پرنٹ عریضہ۔۳ {Print Ariza-3}]", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 1}, {"Id": 1016960, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Mohaddis e Noori says: The letter of supplication to Imam Mahdi (a) has been narrated in various ways and is available in the books of supplication; but the manuscript which I have is not found in any of those books, not even in the chapter Mazaar from Bihar ul Anwaar. There has been made no indication towards this letter even in the chapter of supplication from Bihar ul Anwaar , wherein an attempt was made to collect all the supplications. As this narration has not been mentioned very often, I felt it compulsory to narrate it here. A profound scholar, Mohammad bin Mohammad Tayyib, a cleric of the Safavid Period, narrates the following text in his book named Anees ul Aabideen , from the book As Sa-aadaat…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Marhoom Mahaddis-e-Noori kehte hai: Hazrat Imam-e-Asr (a) ki khidmat mein isteghasa aur ariza ke mutaddid tareeqe riwaayat huwe hai, aur dua ki kitaab ke andar jo keh logo’n ke darmiyaan raaej hai maujood hai, lekin ek nuskha jo un kitaab mein mawjood nahi hai yahan tak Mazaar Bihaar-ul-Anwaar jis mein duaawo’n aur arizo’n ko jama kiya gaya hai wahan bhi nahi hai, chun-keh iska nuskha bohot hi kam nazar aata hai is liye isko ham yahan zikr kar rahe hai. Buzurg Faazil Muhammad bin Muhammad Tayyab Safavi jin ka shumaar hukumat ke ulma mein hota hai kitaab Anees-ul-Aabedeen mein kitaab Al-Saadaat se naql karte hai. Mohim haajaat ke liye dua-e-Tawassul yeh hai…", "UrduDescription": "مرحوم محدث نوری کہتے ہیں کہ استغاثہ کے عریضہ کی حضرت حجت کیلئے متعدد طریقوں سے روایت ہوئی ہے اور دعاؤں کی کتابوں میں کہ جو لوگوں کے درمیان موجود ہے لیکن جو نسخہ اس کتاب میں موجود نہیں ہے یہاں تک کہ مزار میں (بحار الانوار) اور دعاؤں اور عریضہ کی کتابوں میں بھی ذکر نہیں ہے چونکہ اس کا نسخہ کم یاب ہے اس لئے اس کو یہاں نقل کرتاہوں محمد بن طیب صفویہ حکومت کے علماء میں سے ہے اس نے اپنی کتاب انیس العابدین میں کتاب السعادات سے اس طرح نقل کیا ہے دعائے توسل مہم امور اور حوائج کے لئے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016961, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the name of Allah, the Beneficent, the Merciful I seek means through You O Abal Qasim, Mohammad bin al-Hasan bin Ali bin Mohammad bin Ali bin Musa bin Jafar bin Mohammad bin Ali bin al-Husain bin Ali bin Abi Talib, the great news, the straight path, the firm rope, the reliable shelter. And through Your mother, the Mistress of all the ladies of the Worlds, and through Your purified predecessors, and your holy mothers, through Yaseen and the wise Quran, and the great sublimity, and the truth of faith, and the light of the light, and the hidden book, that You become my ambassador towards Almighty Allah to fulfill the demand of so and so, or to destroy so and so. O Saeed bin Othman, and O Mohammad bin Othman, deliver our incident to the Master of the Time, peace be upon him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "تَوَسَّلْتُ اِلَیْكَ یَا اَبَالْقَاسِمِ مُحَمَّدَ بْنِ الْحَسَنِ بْنِ عِلِیِّ بْنِ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِیِّ بْنِ مُوْسَی بْنِ جَعْفَرِ بْنِ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِیِّ بْنِ الْحُسَیْنِ بْنِ عَلِیِّ بْنِ اَبِیْ طَالِبٍ، اَلنَّبَاِ الْعَظِیْمِ، اَلصِّرَاطِ الْمُسْتَقِیْمِ، وَعِصْمَۃِ الْلّٰا جِیْنَ۔ بِاُمِّكَ سَیِّدَۃِ نِسَائِ الْعَالَمِیْنَ، وَبِآبَائِكَ الطَّاهِرِیْنَ، وَبِاُمَّهَاتِكَ الطَّهِرَاتِ، بِیَاسِیْنَ وَالْقُرْآنِ الْحَكِیْمِ، وَالْجَبَرُوْتِ الْعَظِیْمِ، وَحَقِیْقَۃِ الْاِیْمَانِ، نُوْرِ النُّوْرِ، وَكِتَابٍ مَّسْطُوْرٍ، اَنْ تَكُوْنَ سَفِیْرِیْ اِلَی اللهِ تَعَالٰی فِی الْحَاجَۃِ لِفُلَانٍ، اَوْهَلَاكِ فُلَانِ بْبِ فُلَانٍ۔ یَا سَعِیْدَ بْنَ عُثْمَانَ، وَیَا مُحَمَّدَ بْنَ عُثْمَانَ، اَوْ صِلَاقِصَّتِیْ اِلٰی صَاحِبَ الزَّمَانِ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَیْهِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null,